  19 Sep 2006; William L. Thomson Jr. <wltjr@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  ChangeLog Initial ebuilds for Jaybird JDBC driver for Firebird SQL databases
  which will replace the existing jdbc(2-3)-firebird ebuilds.

